04021,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ad2b07764aab1caf0913bc3f05e390179364e43","tid":2104021,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d3c7f37ac60fae64211ae457937724f6b810e6","tid":2104021,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"最近見到佢個衛星page (bio果個)叫人唔好迫人戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"用埋啲研究話口罩隔唔到菌<br />\n美國啲人都唔會帶<br />\n咪就係唔帶啲飛沫中撚哂美國先死咁多人囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"戴唔戴罩已經講到口都臭撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如何柏良講睇下邊個笑到最後<br />\n個答案都好明顯下都仲要包拗頸黎突顯自己與別不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都廢9事駁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0206c17ddb61b9757f82b841568037c829450446","tid":2104021,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"頂 迷雲黨呢個term好幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f5bc86d0633cbb50164c61ac91e8d3c6a2e103","tid":2104021,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c70965e5cabddece83b2da7f3af86df223fe88c7","tid":2104021,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">2.）</span>另外，佢哋亦會<span class=\"red\">熱狗式放負</span>，無論你做乜佢地都會揾到嘢鬧，最好乜都唔好做，因為唔做就自然唔會出錯，所以佢地會叫人投白票，因為咩都唔做，正合極權所需（所以白兵思想同理）而如果真係咩都唔做，佢哋又會笑你咩都唔做，雞蛋挑骨頭就係熱狗式放負嘅一大特色<br />\n<br />\n（依照經驗所得，發現<span class=\"red\">呢類人同時亦可能係思維唔發達而周圍放負嘅on9</span>，正正係因為自己解答唔到革命難題，又想急功近利，提出一啲不切實際嘅要求（eg. 200萬人勇武，放諸全世界嘅stat都係冇可能）。當人哋解釋完/ 鬧完自己又駁唔到，但又接受唔到人地批評自己，老羞成怒，開始一味笑人「一講乜乜就屌人乜乜」，<span class=\"gold\">最後變成一個好嬲好嬲，然後上連登笑人好嬲好嬲嘅冷氣軍師</span>，從中獲得「眾人皆醉我獨醒」嘅心理優越&amp;安慰感。由呢一刻開始，思維因心態而扭曲，言論亦變成放負為主而無實質上嘅建議，呢類人即使本身唔係五毛，但行徑上已經同五毛無異。）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">For example:</span><br />\n<br />\n五毛/ 弱能思維on9：<br />\n1.）繼續快樂抗爭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你班廢柴剩係買嘢就可以打倒共產黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.）成班和理非去shopping 就當自己出咗一份力，當手足condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.）叫你衝又唔敢衝學咩人搞革命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">再次重申我唔係話咁就乜都唔去理乜都唔支持，而係大家都應該要有返個正常嘅批判性思維去諗嘢</span>"},{"pid":"1e51d9ccc843bcb7eca242a6ee1308afa7e74060","tid":2104021,"uid":287048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"35+初選成功與否嘅關鍵，係落敗者及其支持者嘅取態<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2103926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2103926</a>"},{"pid":"6445afb92a431c45fe13ae3a577c218ff24c3ad4","tid":2104021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d582fac726780304d688bc1708a09db5ffbc80e","tid":2104021,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"成班反社會人格既失敗者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"社會地底泥"},{"pid":"37be7c8e29e1141b86d8674925ef8dc0da2df76c","tid":2104021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42aa49d231bfd02eecc8870400852531722e74d6","tid":2104021,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"一邊屌人黃圈，一邊搞乜好人經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"根本無人理佢地"},{"pid":"c1503edb3f1b124981d04018212b8f75bf463b28","tid":2104021,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:20:39.000Z","msg":"迷雲=藍"},{"pid":"eb3ff444b603558a7cb1f07019ca0bee3f586cc9","tid":2104021,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"唔明樓主做乜咁勞氣，云黨呢班過氣人士，除左圍爐打飛機，仲可以做乜？不如祝福下国屍去書展中武肺好過啦"},{"pid":"0db69e0a8e2dd3cb0b7a8f9973f00072f86d03ed","tid":2104021,"uid":119291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"推"}]}